window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Piper has been crushing on Ryder Williams for years....</p> <p>What better chance to make her move on him than when he’s sacrificing himself on an auction block for a squealing mass of fans at a charity event? Too bad she’d rather hide in the bathroom than raise her paddle; what girl actually bids on a guy who doesn’t know she exists?</p> <p>Not. Piper.</p> <p>But that's what friends are for....</p> <p>One meddling best friend, and an overpriced bid later, and Ryder Willams is Piper's for the taking. Too bad that she has no intention of collecting on his debt.</p> <p>Too bad Ryder is determined to find out why.</p> <p><b>Note: </b><b><i>Switch Bidder </i></b><b>is a short #JockHard novella, at 10,000 words - aka short novella.</b></p>"; 
